<Link id="l00054" /><CodeLine lineNumber="54"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00055" /><CodeLine lineNumber="55"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// sliceable&#95;expr = &#39;&#42;&#123;&#39; number &#39;&#125;&#39; load&#95;addr&#95;expr &#91;slice&#93;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00056" /><CodeLine lineNumber="56"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                | &#39;(&#39; expr &#39;)&#39; &#91;slice&#93;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00057" /><CodeLine lineNumber="57"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                | ident&#95;expr &#91;slice&#93;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00058" /><CodeLine lineNumber="58"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///                | number &#91;slice&#93;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00059" /><CodeLine lineNumber="59"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00060" /><CodeLine lineNumber="60"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// slice = &#39;&#91;&#39; high-bit-index &#39;:&#39; low-bit-index &#39;&#93;&#39;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00061" /><CodeLine lineNumber="61"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00062" /><CodeLine lineNumber="62"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// load&#95;addr&#95;expr = symbol</span></CodeLine>
